<br>
So if I had the choice to get a warrior with 200 aa, change my religion so I can wear cultural armor/or the option to get better gear without being in a AOW capable guild or on such a crowded server, and more keys and flags I would say I would stay warrior.<br>
<br>
If not I would probably take a 65 bard.<br>
<br>
<br>
I quit my warrior because this would take me a year of boring @#%$, and I would not leave my guild for better loot. More a high end issue than a class issue really. <br>
